## Files to Modify (12 files, CSS-only except minor JSX label additions)

### 1. `index.html` — Font import swap
- Replace `DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600` with `Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700`

### 2. `src/styles/variables.css` — Full token overhaul
- **Panel colors → dark charcoal:** `--color-panel-bg: #1E2028`, `--color-surface-elevated: #2E3140`
- **Text → light-on-dark:** `--color-text-primary: #E8EAED`, secondary `#9AA0AE`, tertiary `#6B7280`
- **Borders → white-alpha:** `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` instead of `#D9D9D4`
- **Accent brighter:** `#10B981` with stronger subtle bg `rgba(16,185,129,0.12)`
- **Danger → lighter red for dark bg:** `#F87171`
- **Toolbar height:** 52px → 56px (more breathing room)
- **Font:** `'Outfit'` replaces `'DM Sans'`
- **New tokens:** `--radius-xs: 4px`, `--space-xxl: 32px`, `--ease-spring`, `--duration-smooth: 0.3s`
- Canvas (`--color-background`) stays `#FAFAF8` — light for blueprint readability

### 3. `src/styles/global.css` — Dark theme globals
- Body background → `var(--color-panel-bg)` (dark wraps light canvas)
- Scrollbar thumbs → `rgba(255,255,255,0.15)` for dark panels
- Selection highlight → new accent color
- Focus ring → new accent

### 4. `src/ui/Toolbar.jsx` — Minimal JSX additions (NO logic changes)
- Add `<span className={styles.groupLabel}>Tools</span>` before tool palette items
- Add group labels "Panels" and "Display" in the last group (wrapping in sub-divs)
